@NODE "Events Review"
@PREV "FAQ"
@NEXT "Copyright notices"
@TOC "Main"


  @{B}Events Review
  @{U}                                                                             @{UU}@{UB}


  @{B}The most useful qualifiers that can be used:@{UB}

  lamiga, lcommand           Left Amiga key
  ramiga, rcommand           Right Amiga key

  lshift                     Left shift key
  rshift                     Right shift key
  shift                      Either of the shift keys

  capslock, caps_lock        Caps lock key
  caps                       Either of the shift keys or caps lock key

  lalt                       Left alt key
  ralt                       Right alt key
  alt                        Either of the alt keys

  ctrl, control              Control key

  numpad, numeric_pad        Key on the numeric pad

  lbutton, left_button       Left mouse button
  mbutton, middle_button     Middle mouse button
  rbutton, right_button      Right mouse button


  @{B}The most useful highmap strings that can be used:@{UB}

  space                      Space key
  backspace                  Backspace key
  tab                        Tab key
  enter                      Enter key (on numeric pad)
  return                     Return key
  del                        Delete key
  up, down, right, left      Arrow keys
  f1-f10                     Functions keys
  help                       Help key

@ENDNODE

